{"tid":2445741,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有拜登政府官員指華府透過多種渠道與北韓接觸但未獲回應","createTime":"2021-03-14T00:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T05:06:19.000Z","uid":39464,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dc48378c1b07bcc2e2d1ebc4ca5168752d1b1806","tid":2445741,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T00:58:42.000Z","msg":"外電引述美國拜登政府高層官員指，華府2月以來透過多種渠道與北韓政府進行幕後的外交接觸，包括北韓駐聯合國代表等，但至今仍未獲平壤當局的任何回應。官員指，美國和北韓已經有一年多沒有進行積極對話，即使美國多次嘗試接觸，但仍未獲回應。官員拒絕猜測平壤當局的沉默，會如何影響拜登政府審視北韓政策。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2382905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2382905&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfFKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=935e39ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2382905</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-northkorea/exclusive-north-korea-unresponsive-to-behind-the-scenes-biden-administration-outreach-u-s-official-idUSKBN2B50P1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-northkorea%2Fexclusive-north-korea-unresponsive-to-behind-the-scenes-biden-administration-outreach-u-s-official-idUSKBN2B50P1&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfFKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=b6381b01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-northkorea%2Fexclusive-north-korea-unresponsive-to-behind-the-scenes-biden-administration-outreach-u-s-official-idUSKBN2B50P1&h=1781851c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-northkorea/exclusive-north-korea-unresponsive-to-behind-the-scenes-biden-administration-outreach-u-s-official-idUSKBN2B50P1</a>"},{"pid":"8a932350d38b1e3d88fe6ebc673c615eb0fe68c4","tid":2445741,"uid":254383,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T00:59:46.000Z","msg":"叫呀侵幫手囉，一定覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"